<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.5.10">
<l>kaḷḷattāl māvaliyai mūvaṭimaṇ koṇṭaḷantāṉ</l>
<l>veḷḷattāṉ vēṅkaṭattā ṉeṉparāl kāṇēṭī</l>
<l>veḷḷattāṉ vēṅkaṭattā ṉēluṅ kalikaṉṟi</l>
<l>yuḷḷatti ṉuḷḷē yuḷaṉkaṇṭāy cāḻalē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>See, Friend! Having taken three feet of earth by fraud from Māvali,</l>
<l rend="indent">he who measured [the world],</l>
<l>They say, indeed, is the one in a flood and the one on Vēṅkaṭam.</l>
<l>You see [this]! Even if he is the one in a flood and the one on Vēṅkaṭam,</l>
<l>He is the one in Kalikaṉṟi’s heart. Cāḻalē!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
